It was great to get back to what I know I’m meant to do. The @sgsplannerconference made me feel like I need to return to my community. The Planner Community. It was humbling to see women with whom I share the same interests and reflect on all the things that can make us great by applying pressure to what we are all good at. It was a remarkable experience, and I’m happy that I was able to be a part of it.
